{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC07_MAR_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "This ruin is amazing... We don't even have a structure this big back home."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It seems like it's been completely abolished, but I wonder if this area used to be a center for alchemy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Marion, shall we get going?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Going? But we just got here.<CR>The real investigation starts now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "However, I mean..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, sorry. You don't like heights."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I can eat any food, and I can fight anyone or anything, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I still do not like high places."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "If you want, you can just go over there and take a rest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "No, I will not leave your side.<CR>I am your bodyguard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Even so, you're looking pretty pale."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I'll just take a closer look and...<CR>Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Someone is coming."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hello. Are you investigating the tunnel or something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it's you. You surprised me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I am relieved..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Did I scare you two?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry, Linca won't be of much use today, so I was just on high alert."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "...This place doesn't necessarily have anything out of the ordinary, but it's very interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I wonder how they were able to make such a big structure..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "People from the past were amazing.<CR>If this place didn't exist..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Riesengang and my workshop would've been cutoff from the outside world."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "That's right... A structure as big as this is being treated like it's just a road..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Riesengang is just a stone quarry now, and they don't seem to care about the relics of the past."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "If you can put things from the past to good use, the quality of life around here would increase dramatically."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I've never thought about that before. I think everyone is satisfied with their lives now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "It's not the easiest, but as long as you don't try to live in luxury, you'll be fine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "To live modestly with what you have now... I guess that's one way to go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I guess there's no limit if you keep looking up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Just like success for an official."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Yup. A gofer will always be a gofer,<CR>no matter how hard I work!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x99,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Oh, darn it! I don't feel like working now! It's not like my salary is increasing, either!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Umm, so why are you investigating the ruins?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x9b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, it's kinda like an investigation for an investigation. First, I have to investigate which ruins have what."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "I'm investigating worthwhile ruins and reporting them to the experts who'll come in the future."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "I see. So you're doing all the backstage preparations..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Seriously. Even I think I'm doing a tedious job, but someone has to do it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "I know perfectly well that you are a brilliant person, Marion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, thanks. I guess I can't pout after hearing that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Well, let's do a bit more work then."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Understood. Ayesha, we will see you later."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "(Being an official is a hard job.<CR>I need to at least try not to get<CR>in their way.)"
        }
    ]
}